item.title: FindNUS :telescope:
item.description: What is FindNUS? FindNUS is a lost and found web application that my pal Jin Xuan and I built over summer 2022. FindNUS was awarded the highest level of achivement, given to only the top 7% of teams (top 29 of 414 teams) for NUS School of Computing’s 2022 iteration of Orbital, an independent software development module. We built FindNUS because we felt that the current lost and found website in NUS sucks and we could do better.
